import React from 'react'
import { Provider } from 'react-redux'
import { BrowserRouter, Route, Switch } from 'react-router-dom'
import HomeMac from "./pages/Home/HomeMac"
import store from './store'
import FinderMac from "./pages/File/FinderMac";
import HomeWindows from "./pages/Home/HomeWindows"
class App extends React.Component {
  render() {
    return (
      <Provider store={store}>
        <BrowserRouter>
          <Switch>
            <Route path="/" exact component={HomeMac}/>
            <Route path="/mac" exact  component={HomeMac}/>
            <Route path="/mac/home" component={HomeMac}/>
            <Route path="/mac/finder" component={FinderMac}/>
            <Route path="/win" exact  component={HomeWindows}/>
          </Switch>
        </BrowserRouter>
      </Provider>
    )
  }
}

export default App
